Terex files to offer seven mln common shrs . Terex Corp filed Friday with the Securities and Exchange Commission to sell up to seven million common shares . Of the total amount , the company will offer five million shares for sale while selling stockholders will offer two million commom shares , Terex said in the filing . After the offering , outstanding shares will total 18 , 646 , 699 common . The company granted the underwriters a 30 - day overallotment option to purchase up to 700 , 000 additional shares . The offering will be led Credit Suisse First Boston . Net proceeds will be used to redeem a portion of senior secured notes . Based in Westport , Conn . , Terex is a global manufacturer of a broad range of construction and mining related capital equipment . 
